stories.title: Doug Marillier on the second one-day international against New Zealand
stories.summary:
Doug Marillier made his international debut in this match and
played a valuable part, opening the batting with Alistair
Campbell and contributing 27 to a partnership of 83

stories.title: Hard work watching Black Caps on the losing end
stories.summary: I haven't been a very good watcher while seeing the CLEAR Black Caps get beaten in the one-day series by Zimbabwe

stories.title: 2nd ODI, Zimbabwe v New Zealand, Statistical Highlights
stories.summary: It was the 1628th ODI in cricket history

stories.title: Ragged Kiwis given working over
stories.summary:
It is difficult to recall a more ragged looking performance than that in
Bulawayo which represented New Zealand's effort in its 21-run loss to
Zimbabwe
